{"title":"账户","icon":"account","grey":true,"shareable":true,"id":"guide/account/index","author":"Mr.Hope","cite":[],"content":[{"tag":"text","type":"info","header":"统一身份认证","path":"guide/account/authorize/index","text":["学校为每位师生提供了一个专属的校园账号。","该账户是您在校期间进行各类线上操作的统一凭证，可用于登录校园网、访问各类教学与服务系统（如“智慧东师”平台、选课系统）、查询成绩课表、图书借阅、校园卡消费记录等。"]},{"tag":"list","header":"校园邮箱","items":[{"text":"邮箱介绍","icon":"intro","path":"guide/account/mail/intro"},{"text":"邮箱客户端设置","icon":"email","path":"guide/account/mail/client"}]},{"tag":"list","header":"企业微信","items":[{"text":"企业号介绍","icon":"wechat","path":"guide/account/wechat/intro"},{"text":"企业号认证","icon":"authorize","path":"guide/account/wechat/authorize"},{"text":"手机号更改","icon":"phone","path":"guide/account/wechat/change"}]}],"time":"2025 年 7 月 23 日 09:43:28"}